thread.title: Claudia

author: Claudia
title: Claudia
text:
Steve at Wetdog Design did a fantastic job designing the invites for my 21st birthday. They were unique, sophisticated and incorporated all the fine details that I have ever wanted for my 21st invite. Steve also ensured that I had a great customer experience. He was prompt with emails, answered any questions I had and produced proofs until I was happy with the end product, an experience you don't really get through other online services. Delivery of the invites was also very speedy. The professionalism at Wetdog is a winner for me, and I will definitely be recommending him to all my Melbourne friends. For any future invites, I know where i'll be going!!
Thank you Wetdog Designs, and Steve, for all the help and the amazing invitations!
